  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  primary AML（except APL patients）;

          -  ECOG PS:0-2

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  AML patient who has already received induction treatment, no matter what the outcome
             is;

          -  Treatment-related AML;

          -  Active cancer patients who's condition need to be treated;

          -  The one with serious infectious diseases（eg.uncontrolled tuberculosis or invasive
             pulmonary aspergillosis）

          -  Active heart disease.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
